prompt.title: Embedding for Avoiding Fraudulent Costume Jewelry Scams
prompt.content: There has been an increase in fraudulent and harmful costume jewelry appearing on the market during the current economic crisis, as people try to save money. Korálky Katlas has prepared a summary of things to watch out for when purchasing finished costume jewelry and jewelry-making components, based on reports from customers about problems and scams they've encountered both in the Czech Republic and abroad.
